### Tech Stack Used
This project is built using a standard **Full-Stack architecture**.

| Component | Technology | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend (Client)** | **HTML5, CSS3, JavaScript** | Handles the UI, data rendering, and client-side validation. |
| **Backend (Server)** | Assumed **Node.js with Express.js** (or similar framework) | Provides the REST API and handles business logic. |
| **Database (Data)** | Assumed **MongoDB** or **MySQL/PostgreSQL** | Stores all user records. |


